<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/25399772">通过这张图是否可以判断出是持枪还是对讲机？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2342559" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"><a href="http://henan.youth.cn/gdxw/201409/t20140917_5752573.htm" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">河南县官对话群众，警察持枪撑伞护卫？“是对讲机”<i class="icon-external"></i></a><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/2c6bd80cffd619145fe1ec7593904e8c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="304" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/2c6bd80cffd619145fe1ec7593904e8c_r.jpg"></div>


